# Serve the prerendered shell for dynamic client routes so a direct
# hit (refresh, shared link) hydrates instead of 404ing; SolidStart's
# router picks up the real path from the URL. Format is
# `<source> <destination> <status>`, status 200 = rewrite. Keep the
# trailing slash on the destination: shells are emitted as
# `<route>/index.html`, and Workers Assets 301s bare directory paths
# to the slashed form, clobbering the original URL.

/studio/:id  /studio/  200
